Install packages

library(dplyr)
library(tidyverse)
library(tidytext)
library(feather)
library(koRpus)
library(childesr)

Plot

sample_measure <- read_feather("/Users/Yawen/Desktop/lexical diversity/trial6_childes/sample_measure.feather")

# All children
sample_measure %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = length, y = value, color = age))+
  geom_smooth(se=F)+
  facet_grid(~measure)+
  theme_classic()+
  labs(title = "Points of Stabilization",
       subtitle = "At Different Age")

sample_measure %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = length, y = value, color = group))+
  geom_smooth(se=F)+
  facet_grid(age~measure)+
  theme_classic()+
  labs(title = "Points of Stabilization",
       subtitle = "UK&US children")

# plot 3 sampled children
set.seed(100)
sample_id <- sample(x=unique(sample_measure$subject), 3)

sample_measure %>%
  filter(subject %in% sample_id)%>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = length, y = value, color=measure))+
  geom_smooth(se=F)+
  facet_grid(age~measure)+
  theme_classic()+
  labs(title = "Points of Stabilization",
       subtitle = "Sampled children at 20 and 40 months")

sample_measure %>%
  filter(subject %in% sample_id)%>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = length, y = value, color=measure))+
  geom_point()+
  facet_grid(age~measure)+
  theme_classic()+
  labs(title = "Points of Stabilization",
       subtitle = "Sampled children at 20 and 40 months")
